@startuml reception_sequence
!theme plain
title Reception Sequence Diagram - Patient Registration & Edit Management

actor Reception
participant "System" as sys
participant "Database" as db
participant "Notification" as notif

== Login ==
Reception -> sys: Login
sys -> db: Validate Credentials
db -> sys: Return User Data
sys -> Reception: Display Dashboard

== Register New Patient ==
Reception -> sys: Register New Patient
sys -> Reception: Display Registration Form
Reception -> sys: Submit Patient Data
sys -> sys: Generate Patient ID (PAT####)
sys -> db: Insert Patient Record
db -> sys: Return Patient ID
sys -> notif: Notify General Doctors
sys -> Reception: Registration Success

== Search Patient ==
Reception -> sys: Search Patient
Reception -> sys: Enter Search Criteria (name/ID/phone)
sys -> db: Query Patient Records
db -> sys: Return Search Results
sys -> Reception: Display Patient List

== Request Patient Edit ==
Reception -> sys: Select Patient
Reception -> sys: Request Patient Edit
Reception -> sys: Enter Edit Reason
sys -> db: Create Edit Request
sys -> db: Store Original Patient Data
db -> sys: Return Request ID
sys -> Reception: Edit Request Submitted

== Submit Patient Changes ==
Reception -> sys: View Edit Requests
sys -> db: Query My Edit Requests
db -> sys: Return Request List
sys -> Reception: Display Requests

alt Request Approved for Edit
  Reception -> sys: Edit Patient Data
  sys -> Reception: Display Edit Form with Original Data
  Reception -> sys: Submit Changes
  sys -> db: Store Proposed Changes
  sys -> db: Update Request Status to 'changes_submitted'
  db -> sys: Confirm Update
  sys -> Reception: Changes Submitted for Final Approval
else Request Not Approved
  sys -> Reception: Request Still Pending
end

@enduml